            },
            {
              "id": 522197,
              "key": "aa48f29c-7e40-445c-85c8-deae6afaf3f8",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "What does it mean that there is no solution? How can that be?\n\nTry sketching the lines. What do you see?",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 578210,
              "key": "56edd6e3-56a3-489f-a140-d66cc838bc47",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "ImageAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "url": "https://video.udacity-data.com/topher/2018/March/5abc2f3f_screen-shot-2018-03-28-at-5.11.09-pm/screen-shot-2018-03-28-at-5.11.09-pm.png",
              "non_google_url": "https://s3.cn-north-1.amazonaws.com.cn/u-img/56edd6e3-56a3-489f-a140-d66cc838bc47",
              "caption": "",
              "alt": "",
              "width": 300,
              "height": 400,
              "instructor_notes": null
            },
            {
              "id": 578211,
              "key": "1c87cdb2-ad07-4611-810a-95c844a10ad4",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "Since these two line are in parallel, they do not intersect, therefore, there is no solution. (As there is not a point  on the plot that will satisfy both equations simultaneously). ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 578215,
              "key": "2ccabf2a-af12-41bc-9b3f-eb266f83aba9",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "As a comparison, the two lines in the plot below represent two independent linear equations with one solution.\nThe solution will be the point on the graph (here in the blue x) satisfying both equations. ",
              "instructor_notes": ""
            },
            {
              "id": 578212,
              "key": "20c5f2c7-179b-4c9b-a455-17a8450df2cf",
